title: Ubehage's EasyCopy v2.3.1
description:
Ubehage's EasyCopy v2.3.1
-------------------------
"Small, Fast and Easy to use!"

Here is an update to this user- and nerd-friendly tool for copying/moving around with files and folders.
This one fixes a critical error, that was just recently found!


Fixes in this release:
- Would not read from write-protected media.
- Could not cancel a job when asked to overwrite existing files.
